Pay atention to R6910-13.
If all good, remove U6903 and resolder its pads.
Change it, if still same problem persists.

title: 820-01987-A  no power 5 volt
message:
PPVIN_G3H_P3V3G3HRTC_R  is a VIN voltage, derived from PPBUS_G3H.
12.6V is the correct voltage, when MLB is in good working condition.

If you don't get L6900 voltage with charger, why would you expect it on battery alone?
